{"tid":1725043,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"各區投票站地址公佈咗喇,  大家快啲去 check 吓自己個投票站係邊度","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:19:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea50151abdfaafc6eef70a785b230093e97a4046","tid":1725043,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:37:52.000Z","msg":"各區投票站地址公佈咗喇,  大家快啲去 check 吓自己個投票站係邊度<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fchi%2Fp_cs.html&d=1ryX%2BwltUSTIgmnFzyWg%2BBAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=65b3444e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n投票站與點票站<br />\n中西區<br />\n灣仔區<br />\n東區<br />\n南區<br />\n油尖旺區<br />\n深水埗區<br />\n九龍城區<br />\n黃大仙區<br />\n觀塘區<br />\n荃灣區<br />\n屯門區<br />\n元朗區<br />\n北區<br />\n大埔區<br />\n西貢區<br />\n沙田區<br />\n葵青區<br />\n離島區<br />\n<br />\n請點擊 地理資訊地圖和其中的&quot;2019年區議會一般選舉投票站&quot;，然後輸入投票站編號(例如:A0101)以參閱該投票站的資料。 <br />\n<br />\n專用投票站"},{"pid":"a860bc1bb38375c2582e35d930e4031c420004dc","tid":1725043,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:47:19.000Z","msg":"11月24日 星期日 就係投票日<br />\n<br />\n9 日後咋<br />\n<br />\n請及早準備"},{"pid":"3f16b9dd33657d33c86151e08c7c8957cf92ab7b","tid":1725043,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T23:35:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"936cddcbba0ddcbdedfe6aa0a75241069f94e224","tid":1725043,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T00:37:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6a56d5c0fa31c1acadb0085ef5effe7586ca70c7","tid":1725043,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"962dac40669466551cd82aec9a08572dfa3c5227","tid":1725043,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:12:12.000Z","msg":"嗰朝要早D投, 我會排開站投<img src=\